Setup wxWidgets for VS in windows.
1. Download wxWidget source code. unzip the file. 
2. Copy to D:/sdks.
3. Open wxWidgets/build/msw/wx_vc#.sln
4. Batch build -> Select all 
5. Environment varibles -> New system variables -> Variable name: WXWIN; Varable value: D:\sdks\wxWidets.
6. Open VS -> new C++ windows desktop application -> Delete all Header files, Resource files Source Files.
7. Open Project properties -> C/C++ Additional Include Directories: $(WXWIN)\include;$(WXWIN)\include\msvc
   ->Linker Addiitional Library Directories: $(WXWIN)\lib\vc_lib

